      "body_text": "*We do not have enough information to find the cause of this issue.*\\n\\nWhile the lag occurs, please press `F3` + `L` once, then wait a short moment until profiling has finished.Afterwards, please **attach the generated **`.zip` file containing the profiling results here. The file path is shown in chat; the file can be found in minecraft/debug/profiling/<DATE>.zip.\\n\\nIf you are playing on a server please additionally run the command `/perf start` to create a profiling report for the server. In case you do not have the permission to run this command, make sure that you're a server operator.Once profiling has finished, please **attach the generated **`.zip` file from `debug/profiling/<DATE>.zip` of the server folder.\\n\\nThis issue is being temporarily resolved as **Awaiting Response**. Once the requested information has been delivered, the report will be reopened automatically.*Quick Links*:📓 Bug Tracker Guidelines -- 💬 Community Support -- 📧 Mojang Support (Technical Issues) -- 📧 Microsoft Support (Account Issues) -- 📓 Project Summary -- ✍️ Feedback and Suggestions -- 📖 Game Wiki\\n\\n",
      "body_length": 1100,
      "rendered_body": "<p><em>We do not have enough information to find the cause of this issue.</em></p>\n\n<p>While the lag occurs, please press <tt>F3</tt> + <tt>L</tt> once, then wait a short moment until profiling has finished.<br>\nAfterwards, please <b>attach the generated</b> <tt>.zip</tt> file containing the profiling results here. The file path is shown in chat; the file can be found in <a href=\"https://minecrafthopper.net/help/finding-minecraft-data-folder/\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">minecraft/debug/profiling/&lt;DATE&gt;.zip</a>.</p>\n\n<p>If you are playing on a server please additionally run the command <tt>/perf start</tt> to create a profiling report for the server. In case you do not have the permission to run this command, make sure that you're a server operator.<br>\nOnce profiling has finished, please <b>attach the generated</b> <tt>.zip</tt> file from <tt>debug/profiling/&lt;DATE&gt;.zip</tt> of the server folder.</p>\n\n<p>This issue is being temporarily resolved as <b>Awaiting Response</b>. Once the requested information has been delivered, the report will be reopened automatically.<br>\n<em>Quick Links</em>:<br>\n📓 <a href=\"https://aka.ms/MCBugTrackerHelp\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Bug Tracker Guidelines</a> – 💬 <a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/minecraft\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Community Support</a> – 📧 <a href=\"https://aka.ms/Minecraft-Support\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Mojang Support (Technical Issues)</a> – 📧 <a href=\"https://support.xbox.com/contact-us/\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Microsoft Support (Account Issues)</a> – 📓 <a href=\"https://report.bugs.mojang.com/servicedesk/customer/portal/2\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Project Summary</a> – ✍️ <a href=\"https://aka.ms/MinecraftFeedbackDiscord\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Feedback and Suggestions</a> – 📖 <a href=\"https://minecraft.wiki/\" class=\"external-link\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Game Wiki</a></p>",
